Section::::Season 8 ( 2019 ) .
UP TV announced season eight on September 25 , 2018 .
It is scheduled to start on January 3 , 2019 , it will feature the birth of Tori and Bobby 's son , Zach and Whitney 's vow renewal , Carlin and Evan 's engagement , and Josie and Kelton 's wedding .
